## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Postman / ThunderClient collections will be written/used to test backend APIs (Auth, Products, Cart, Analytics) before integrating with the frontend.
- Backend routing and endpoints will be validated using explicit cURL or Node scripts simulating edge-cases.

### Manual Verification
- We will manually navigate the frontend to verify:
  1. Successful login and JWT retention.
  2. Smooth cart updates.
  3. Proper checkout flow catching the Stripe test payment lifecycle.
  4. PDF download triggering flawlessly.
  5. Admin views successfully restricting non-admin users and displaying data.
